data.title: Securities (Finance)
data.meta_description: ISJ020 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. ISJ looks at how regulation has been the catalyst for driving change in the payments space and the opportunities this presents for employing new technologies and more innovative strategies across the UK and Europe. ISJ focuses on funds as an extended section this month and looks at the development of custody and securities services over the past decade.
